	End If







	AddScore(25)


	If TrapTurnedON = FALSE then

		Azar = int(rnd*2)
		If azar = 0 then
			AzarSoundGhostVoices()
		Else
			AzarSoundThunder
		End If

	End If


	If DemonOnPlayfield = TRUE and DemonInsideTrap = FALSE then 'If there is a demon on the pf but it is not in the trap... 
	
		AzarVoiceScream()

	End If

	If AngelInsideTRap = TRUE then

		'AzarVoiceScream()

	End If



	


	'Two different QuickShot here? I will explain why.
	'Originally there was only 1 QS to the mistery kicker that lead the ball to the upper PF. It's seems natural, aint?
	'but the problem with that is that "stressed" the player a bit, forcing him to shot for the upper pf.
	'Perhaps u wanted to shot for the portal, or the trap, and if u have the QS urging u to shot for the upper pf and u
	'wanted to shot to the trap... what's happen? I tell ya: stressed players.
	'So there are 2 different QS, one to the upper PF and one for the Lost Soul (the ball will be keeped on the lower pf).
	'let's see if it fits the players tastes :)


	'------------------------------------------------------------------
	'--=[ BLOOD EXTRACTOR MBALL ]=-----
	'------------------------------------------------------------------
	If BloodExtractorMballEnabled = TRUE then

